Package gov.nasa.pds.api.engineering.lexer

Class SearchBaseListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nasa.pds.api.engineering.lexer.SearchBaseListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SearchListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    public class SearchBaseListener
extends Object
implements SearchListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of SearchListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
